        public Action updateVariableWith(Function<V,V> function)

        Creates an action that updates the context variable. A current value of the context variable is given to the function and the result of the function is written back to the context.

        Parameters:
        function - A function to compute a new value of the context variable.
        Returns:
        An action that updates the context variable.
